8\u202f\u20b99,800** | Well under \u20b950,000 \u2013 you could upgrade any line item or add a spa treatment. |\\n\\n*If you travel with a companion sharing the same room, the **per\u2011person** cost halves for accommodation, bringing the total to ~\u20b97,500 each.*\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 5\ufe0f\u20e3 PRACTICAL TRAVEL TIPS\\n\\n| Topic | Recommendation |\\n|-------|----------------|\\n| **Best time to visit** | **Oct\u202f\u2013\u202fFeb** (cool, dry). Monsoon (Jun\u2011Sept) offers lush scenery & lower rates but limited beach activities. |\\n| **Getting there** | Goa International Airport (Dabolim) \u2013 30\u202fmin by taxi to Panaji. Alternatively, Konkan Railway (Madgaon) if you\u2019re coming from Mumbai/Delhi. |\\n| **Local transport** | Rent a **scooter** (\u20b9350\u2011\u20b9450/day). Carry a **helmet** (mandatory). For longer distances, use **Ola/Uber** or pre\u2011book a **private car**. |\\n| **Currency** | ATMs are plentiful in Panaji, Calangute, and Margao. Keep some cash for beach shacks that don\u2019t accept cards. |\\n| **Safety** | Goa is tourist\u2011friendly. Keep an eye on belongings on crowded beaches, especially at night. Drink responsibly; many beach bars have a \u201cno\u2011outside\u2011alcohol\u201d rule. |\\n| **Health** | Stay hydrated, use sunscreen (SPF\u202f30+). Carry basic meds (pain reliever, anti\u2011diarrheal). |\\n| **Cultural etiquette** | Dress modestly when visiting churches and temples. Remove shoes before entering religious sites. |\\n| **Connectivity** | Free Wi\u2011Fi at most hotels and caf\u00e9s. For mobile data, buy a **Jio/Idea prepaid SIM** (\u20b9199 for 2\u202fGB + 28\u202fdays). |\\n| **Packing list** | Light cotton clothing, swimwear, flip\u2011flops, comfortable walking shoes, hat, sunglasses, reusable water bottle, small day\u2011backpack. |\\n\\n---\\n\\n## 6\ufe0f\u20e3 QUICK CHECKLIST BEFORE YOU GO\\n\\n- [ ] Book hotel (choose budget/mid\u2011range/luxury) \u2013 confirm check\u2011in time.  \\n- [ ] Reserve a **scooter** online (many platforms allow advance booking).  \\n- [ ] Pre\u2011pay airport\u2011to\u2011hotel transfer (\u20b9800\u2011\u20b91,200) if arriving late at night.  \\n- [ ] Print or screenshot e\u2011tickets for any water\u2011sport activity you want to pre\u2011book.  \\n- [ ] Pack a small **first\u2011aid kit** (band\u2011aids, antiseptic wipes).  \\n- [ ] Download **Goa Tourism app** for offline maps and event updates.  \\n\\n---\\n\\n### \ud83c\udf89 Your 2\u2011Day Goa adventure is ready!  \\n\\nPick the accommodation tier that feels right, follow the itinerary, and you\u2019ll experience the best of Goa\u2019s beaches, heritage, and nightlife\u2014all comfortably within your **\u20b950,000** budget. Have a fantastic trip! \ud83c\udf34\ud83c\udfd6\ufe0f\ud83d\udea4\",\"type\":\"TextMessage\"}}", "sender": "Travel_Planner_9dad0395-0f59-4232-a2bf-58ca92087960/9dad0395-0f59-4232-a2bf-58ca92087960", "receiver": null, "kind": "MessageKind.PUBLISH", "delivery_stage": "DeliveryStage.DELIVER", "type": "Message"}
